# Project Folder Structure (Monorepo)

This repository has `backend` (Bun + Hono) and `frontend` (Vite + React + Tailwind) workspaces.

```
├── backend/
│   ├── src/
│   │   └── index.ts             # Hono app and routes
│   ├── package.json             # Bun scripts and deps
│   └── tsconfig.json            # Bun + Hono JSX config
│
├── frontend/
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/          # UI components
│   │   ├── hooks/               # Custom hooks
│   │   ├── lib/                 # Utilities
│   │   └── main.tsx             # App bootstrap
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── vite.config.ts           # Vite, React, Tailwind plugins
│   ├── eslint.config.js         # ESLint config
│   └── tsconfig*.json           # TS project configs
│
└── test/
    ├── unit/                    # Unit tests
    └── integration/             # Integration tests
```

## Principles

- Keep backend and frontend concerns isolated
- Use absolute imports via configured aliases where set (e.g., `@` → `src` in frontend)
- Keep shared UI patterns under `src/components/ui` in frontend

## Naming Conventions

- Use kebab-case for files and directories
- Descriptive, self-documenting names limited to ~30 characters

## Module Organization

- One component/hook per file (preferred)
- Group cohesive utilities when appropriate
